      "rationale": "Testing performed under ASTM F1717 protocol at a single rod diameter (5.5 mm) and single interbody spacing (44 mm). While laboratory temperature and humidity were controlled, the single test condition limits coverage of the clinical loading space. Achieved level 2 rather than required level 3; this gap is acknowledged and accepted given the primary validation objective of demonstrating methodology accuracy at the nominal design point."
