      "rationale": "FEA boundary conditions replicate ASTM F1717 fixture geometry to within 0.1 mm. Material properties assigned from same lot certification data used for test specimens. Actuator displacement rate equivalence confirmed. Residual differences between model and physical inputs estimated to contribute <1.5% uncertainty to QoI predictions."
