      "rationale": "All three QoIs (stiffness, yield force, force at 40 mm) satisfy E/uval < 1.96 and percent difference < 10% acceptance criteria. Stiffness: 4.2% difference, E/uval=0.87. Yield force: 6.8% difference, E/uval=1.31. Force at 40 mm: 7.4% difference, E/uval=1.52. Validation metric computed per ASME V&V 40 Section 5.4."
