      "rationale": "The three selected QoIs directly correspond to ASTM F1717 acceptance endpoints used in 510(k) submissions for pedicle screw systems. Construct stiffness predicts in-vivo load sharing; yield force predicts fatigue life initiation; force at 40 mm characterizes post-yield behavior. QoI relevance confirmed by clinical literature review."
