      "rationale": "Validation activity directly tests the non-cannulated 7.5 mm design under the ASTM F1717 protocol that constitutes the COU. The FEA framework validated here is the same framework applied in the regulatory submission. Geometric and loading similarity between validation and COU is high; the single test condition limitation (Test conditions factor) is the only noted departure from full representativeness."
